# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Monorepo track kapsamı:
#   - Botpress/detailagent/        (v9.2 frozen, prod bot)
#   - Botpress/detailagent-ms/     (v10 microservice-ready bot)
#   - retrieval-service/           (Fly.io microservice)
#   - docs/                        (ortak referans dokümanlar)
#   - data/csv/                    (seed kaynağı — botlar ve microservice ortak tüketir)
#   - etl/                         (refresh_data.py)
#   - assets/                      (manuel URL + barcode CSV)
#   - .mcp.json                    (Claude Code MCP config)
#
# Açıkça ignore:
#   - archive/                     (eski çalışmalar, 600MB+)
#   - node_modules/                (her yerde)
#   - .env, secrets                (her yerde)
#   - .adk/, .botpress/            (ADK runtime artifact)
#   - Product Groups/              (eski path ismi)
#   - Scripts/                     (eski path ismi, şimdi etl/)
#   - output/                      (eski path ismi, şimdi data/)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Default: ignore root-level entries, whitelist aşağıda
/*

# Tracked root files
!.gitignore
!.mcp.json.example
!README.md

# .mcp.json local-only (contains project refs / tokens per developer)
.mcp.json

# Whitelisted top-level dirs
!Botpress/
!retrieval-service/
!data/
!etl/
!assets/
!docs/

# Botpress: only detailagent + detailagent-ms
Botpress/*
!Botpress/detailagent/
!Botpress/detailagent/**
!Botpress/detailagent-ms/
!Botpress/detailagent-ms/**

# Global exclusions (every subdir)
**/node_modules/
**/.adk/
**/.botpress/
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/bun.lock
**/package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.DS_Store
**/*.log

# macOS iCloud/Dropbox sync duplicates (e.g. "foo 2.ts", "bar 2.csv")
**/* 2.*
**/* 2
**/.turbo/

# Temporary/inspection scripts (detailagent)
Botpress/detailagent/scripts/_tmp_*

# Runtime artifacts
**/traces*.db
**/traces*.json
**/.adk/bot/traces/

# Local secrets (used only for production secret ops)
.local-secrets/
